CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 15, 1963, p. 15, reads: "The 1963 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama. Pittsburgh's only home and food show, opened before a huge throng last Thursday, June 6, at the spacious Syria Mosque in Oakland...  4. Cloverleaf Dodge: Yvonne Kemp and Joan Hall."
TitMainTitle: Yvonne Jones Kemp and Joan Hall, seated on back of Dodge Dart convertible, with banner inscribed "Here Now 63 Dependables by Dodge," at 1963 Pittsburgh Courier - WAMO, Home-A-Rama fair, Syria Mosque
